{"id":"e315055eb6b598c8b3a74cbd3d954e0b18fd6dcd","url":"https://www.ithome.com/0/979/001.htm","title":"绿厂系首个万级大电池新机：OPPO A7 Pro Max 手机参数曝光，骁龙 4 Gen 5 芯片","site_name":"Info Flow","source":"IT之家 (ITHome)","byline":"作者：潞源","excerpt":"OPPO 首款万级大电池手机 A7 Pro Max 参数曝光，配备 10000mAh 单电芯电池和 80W 快充，搭载骁龙 4 Gen 5 芯片。博主此前透露绿厂万级电池将率先落地中端机。#手机电池# #OPPO新机#","content_html":"<DIV class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><div id=\"paragraph\">\r\n            \r\n            <p data-vmark=\"2fe2\"><a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/\" target=\"_blank\">IT之家</a> 7 月 20 日消息，博主 @数码闲聊站 今天在微博发文，曝光绿厂系首个万级大电池新机 OPPO A7 Pro Max。</p><p data-vmark=\"4e14\"><img src=\"https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/7/b7387aa5-b09a-4bdf-9547-82d2abe9e979.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto\" w=\"958\" h=\"271\" data-snap-from=\"%7B%22from%22%3A%22weibo%22%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F6048569942%2F5322758672354269%22%7D\" data-mpos=\"2,0\" data-vmark=\"ec54\" title=\"绿厂系首个万级大电池新机：OPPO A7 Pro Max 手机参数曝光，骁龙 4 Gen 5 芯片\" data-original=\"https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/7/b7387aa5-b09a-4bdf-9547-82d2abe9e979.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto\" width=\"958\" height=\"232\"></p><p data-vmark=\"80db\">据介绍，这款手机搭载 6.78 英寸 1.5K 120Hz OLED 直屏，<strong>配备骁龙 4 Gen 5（第五代骁龙 4）芯片</strong>，<strong>拥有 10000mAh 单电芯大电池</strong>，支持 80W 快充。配备 5000 万像素前置镜头、5000 万后置主摄、200 万像素辅助镜头，厚度 8.47mm，重量 226g。</p><p data-vmark=\"491d\">后续有用户在评论区询问：“骁龙 7 系列和 8s 系列是不是不更新了？不会砍掉了吧”，博主回复称：“千元机用不起，中端机用户看不上，有点尴尬 <img src=\"https://img.ithome.com/app/emotion/svg/rm_e_goutouxieyan.svg\" title=\"绿厂系首个万级大电池新机：OPPO A7 Pro Max 手机参数曝光，骁龙 4 Gen 5 芯片\" width=\"20\" data-original=\"https://img.ithome.com/app/emotion/svg/rm_e_goutouxieyan.svg\">”；另一名用户则询问道：“完了，<strong>又来一个给畅享 90proMax 助攻的</strong> <img src=\"https://img.ithome.com/app/emotion/svg/rm_e_goutouxieyan.svg\" title=\"绿厂系首个万级大电池新机：OPPO A7 Pro Max 手机参数曝光，骁龙 4 Gen 5 芯片\" width=\"20\" data-original=\"https://img.ithome.com/app/emotion/svg/rm_e_goutouxieyan.svg\">”，博主则回复道：“<img src=\"https://img.ithome.com/app/emotion/svg/rm_e_wulianxiaoku.svg\" title=\"绿厂系首个万级大电池新机：OPPO A7 Pro Max 手机参数曝光，骁龙 4 Gen 5 芯片\" width=\"20\" data-original=\"https://img.ithome.com/app/emotion/svg/rm_e_wulianxiaoku.svg\">”。</p><p data-vmark=\"fa02\"><img src=\"https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/7/5a0327bf-d21c-4217-8524-1de9478d3715.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto\" w=\"961\" h=\"319\" data-snap-from=\"%7B%22from%22%3A%22weibo%22%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F6048569942%2F5322758672354269%22%7D\" data-mpos=\"2,2\" data-vmark=\"a482\" title=\"绿厂系首个万级大电池新机：OPPO A7 Pro Max 手机参数曝光，骁龙 4 Gen 5 芯片\" data-original=\"https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/7/5a0327bf-d21c-4217-8524-1de9478d3715.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto\" width=\"961\" height=\"272\"></p><p data-vmark=\"7130\"><img src=\"https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/7/b396dd28-cf2b-48ba-8cac-f2e443a55282.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto\" w=\"961\" h=\"286\" data-snap-from=\"%7B%22from%22%3A%22weibo%22%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F6048569942%2F5322758672354269%22%7D\" data-mpos=\"2,2\" data-vmark=\"78af\" title=\"绿厂系首个万级大电池新机：OPPO A7 Pro Max 手机参数曝光，骁龙 4 Gen 5 芯片\" data-original=\"https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/7/b396dd28-cf2b-48ba-8cac-f2e443a55282.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto\" width=\"961\" height=\"244\"></p><p data-vmark=\"fb39\"><a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/0/945/397.htm\" target=\"_blank\">据IT之家此前报道</a>，@数码闲聊站 曾在今年 4 月份表示：“阿绿万级大电池也在路上了，先上中端机。”表明 OPPO 将推出 10000mAh 左右电池容量的手机，并且会率先在中端产品落地。</p><p data-vmark=\"a18d\"><img src=\"https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/4/3bc7856d-defa-42c3-9a1d-380087a57941.jpg?x-bce-process=image/auto-orient,o_1\" w=\"696\" h=\"762\" data-vmark=\"24af\" title=\"绿厂系首个万级大电池新机：OPPO A7 Pro Max 手机参数曝光，骁龙 4 Gen 5 芯片\" data-original=\"https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/4/3bc7856d-defa-42c3-9a1d-380087a57941.jpg?x-bce-process=image/auto-orient,o_1\" width=\"696\" height=\"762\"><